  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports Meta Quest 2/3 and Steam VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the quiet of the night, with only a few people on campus, you can freely destroy desks and experience the thrill of doing things you’d never dare to do in real life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy the classroom using bows, machine guns, and swords.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautifully designed Japanese-style campus offers a unique experience like no other.</p>",
